cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.HC 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image emotion classification. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with emotions in images. The use of deep learning suggests it may also belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG). Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible category as the paper deals with classifying images based on their content. Finally, Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) is a possible category as the paper deals with emotions in images, which is a topic relevant to human perception and interaction.
